membership in nato on grounds it is a usled antisoviet 
military alliance he wants a united germany to belong to both the 
warsaw pact and nato 
but fitzwater said gorbachevs summit meeting with bush this 
month and later assurances offered by secretary of state james a 
baker iii may be helping to change gorbachevs mind 
its clear that this is going to be a gradual process i 
cant report any conclusion to the matter but we do feel progress 
is going to be made the spokesman said 
