fujimori wants to visit japan but had not received any official 
notification if fujimori indicates he wants to visit we would 
welcome him and would like to arrange meetings with those people he 
wants to meet he said 
fujimori 51 is the eldest son of japanese emigrants who 
traveled to peru from japans southern island of kyushu in 1934 in 
lima they opened an upholstery shop that failed during a boycott 
of japanese businesses during world war ii 
fujimori earned a degree in agricultural engineering and became 
a school administrator 
japanese emigration peaked in the decades before and after world 
