is that would be fine but he doesnt west said 
baker who has built or owned 54 boats in 30 years said he 
needs just one more berth and a few more weeks on the black river 
before the atlas will be ready to leave port huron forever 
i certainly havent wanted to stir up a hornets nest but the 
spring came so late this year i havent been able to do the work 
thats necessary to get this old girl out of here he said i 
am trying believe me i am trying 
