<TEXT>
sen dave durenberger has brought dishonor 
and disrepute on the senate and should be denounced by his 
colleagues for engaging in unethical conduct the senate ethics 
committees special counsel recommended tuesday 
robert s bennetts recommendation was a surprise on the opening 
