procedures and some minor design modifications in dc10 and 747 
combination passengercargo aircraft 
new planes incorporate the recommendations and manufacturers 
are working to retrofit older aircraft gamble said 
we feel those faa recommendations are adequate he said 
how those changes relate to what the judge ordered we dont 
know 
