us rep donald lukens conviction on a 
charge he had sex with a teenage girl was upheld tuesday by a 
state appeals court 
the 59yearold republican was convicted may 26 1989 of a 
misdemeanor charge of contributing to the unruliness of a minor he 
was accused of paying a girl to have sex with him at his columbus 
apartment in november 1988 when she was 16 
