stocks advanced to nearrecord levels tuesday 
strengthened by a lateafternoon rally that extended mondays gains 
the dow jones average of 30 industrials which rose 3019 points 
on monday gained another 4085 points to 293342 much of that in 
the final hour of trading it was the second highest closing level 
in history eclipsed only by the record 293519 reached june 4 
